OL,3,CMelanoma rates in UK hit highest on
OL,4,Crecord ahead of scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FMore than 20,000 people per year in
OL,7,Fthe UK are now diagnosed with melanoma
OL,8,F` the highest on record, figures show.
OL,10,FMelanoma, which is the deadliest form
OL,11,Fof skin cancer, is caused by
OL,12,Foverexposure to ultraviolet rays from
OL,13,Fthe sun or sunbeds. It is often
OL,14,Fidentified by a smudgy mole.
OL,16,FAhead of the sunny bank holiday
OL,17,Fweekend, which has been forecast to be
OL,18,Fone of the hottest on record, Cancer
OL,19,FResearch UK urged people to enjoy the
OL,20,Fsun safely by covering up and using
OL,21,Fsunscreen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
