OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779494576
OL,3,CMelanoma rates in UK hit highest on
OL,4,Crecord ahead of scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FIts most recent data for the year 2022
OL,7,Fshows there were 20,980 new cases of
OL,8,Fmelanoma, the highest number it has
OL,9,Fever seen.
OL,11,FNew analysis from the charity also
OL,12,Fsuggests the number of people told
OL,13,Fthey have melanoma will reach 26,500 a
OL,14,Fyear by 2040.
OL,16,FThat represents a 23% rise in men and
OL,17,Fa 26% rise in women between now and
OL,18,F2040.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
