PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779494576
OL,3,CMelanoma rates in UK hit highest on
OL,4,Crecord ahead of scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FOverall, women are more likely than
OL,7,Fmen to be diagnosed with melanoma skin
OL,8,Fcancer at younger ages, while men
OL,9,Fexperience the condition more often in
OL,10,Flater life.
OL,12,FHigher rates among younger women tend
OL,13,Fto be linked to sunbathing and sunbed
OL,14,Fuse, while in older men it is long-
OL,15,Fterm exposure to the sun that causes
OL,16,Fharm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
