PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779494576
OL,3,CMelanoma rates in UK hit highest on
OL,4,Crecord ahead of scorching bank holiday
OL,6,FMichelle Mitchell, chief executive of
OL,7,FCancer Research UK, said: "It's
OL,8,Fconcerning to see the rising number of
OL,9,Fpeople being diagnosed with melanoma
OL,10,Fskin cancer across the UK.
OL,12,F"The fact that most of these cases are
OL,13,Fpreventable underlines the importance
OL,14,Fof people taking sun safety seriously.
OL,16,F"Take care when the sun is strong by
OL,17,Fseeking shade, covering up and
OL,18,Fapplying sunscreen and, if you notice
OL,19,Fany unusual changes to your skin,
OL,20,Fcontact your GP.
OL,26,@oD@[OUtD@AOUxD@AOU
