PN,31905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1779494576
OL,3,CMelanoma rates in UK hit highest on
OL,4,Crecord ahead of scorching bank holiday
OL,6,F"Whether it is a new or changing mole,
OL,7,Fa sore that doesn't heal, or an area
OL,8,Fof your skin that looks out of the
OL,9,Fordinary, it's important to get it
OL,10,Fchecked out.
OL,12,F"It probably won't be cancer, but if
OL,13,Fit is, getting it diagnosed and
OL,14,Ftreated early can make all the
OL,15,Fdifference."
OL,17,FCancer Research UK said overdiagnosis,
OL,18,Fwhere cancers that would not go on to
OL,19,Fcause harm are diagnosed, could also
OL,20,Fbe playing a role in rising rates,
OL,21,Falongside increased awareness.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@LO]
